1878584469.text: "Feedback phosphorylation of EGFR at Thr669 by ERK has been found to negatively regulate constitutive EGFR tyrosine kinase activity and HER3 driven Akt activation by suppressing heterodimerization of EGFR and HER3 in lung cancer and triple negative MDA-MB-468 breast cancer cells (Sato etal., 2013; Turke etal., 2012)."
